{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act31side_level_act31side_04_end","storyGroup":"act31side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act31side_level_act31side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HS-4","storyName":"话桑麻","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"几名少年核对了各自发现的异样，种种线索都指向了突然回到大荒城的不速之客。\n另一方面，久别重逢的绩和黍在神农祠前开始了一场长谈。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act31side/level_act31side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act31side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["黍","令","小满","暴躁的天师学徒","天师学徒","绩","左乐","禾生"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_47_g10_fairyfarmland_ex.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_cnclouds","layer":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_saferoom_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":14},{"type":"charslot","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"望不到头的稻田，迷离如幻。天地宽广，却万籁俱寂。","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"一丝酒香飘过，云做旋舞，飘飘然流入一只酒盏。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"仰头饮尽，瞬间天朗气清。","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"嗯......真是一场好梦。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"charslot","id":25},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你怎么有功夫来我这里？","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"你这最近不是很热闹？正好来看看你答应我的高粱酒酿好没有。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你在梦里，我怎么把酒给你？","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你说的是哪一年的酒，这又是你的哪个梦呢？","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"梦里喝不到，让我闻闻味儿也好啊。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"或者是来看看我那个最辛苦的妹妹，最近是不是又累瘦了一点。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"原来这就是小年做出来的奇妙物件？","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":42},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":43},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":44},{"type":"text","text":"诗人挥一挥衣袖，手边便出现一坛酒，两只盏。","id":45},{"type":"text","text":"她抬手拍碎坛口的泥封，陈年酒香霎时蔓延。","id":46},{"type":"text","text":"诗人回身，眺望。稻田绵延百里、万里，春夏秋冬于天空中盘旋，寒来暑往，春去秋来。","id":47},{"type":"dialog","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"这就是你在这颗“心脏”里看到的风景？","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"无尽的稻田，轮转的四季，你每日都在耕作，这儿真能造出你们说的那个东西？","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"需不需要我也来帮你们一把？","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我怕你来了，这个容器也会变成一个大酒缸，或者是突然有了自己的想法，觉得世间不逍遥，不如长梦不醒。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"真的不需要我帮帮？你在这里待了多少年，我都快要记不清了，再不出来走走就怕你憋成我的酒葫芦。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"别的弟弟妹妹，只怕是看不清事里事外，只有你，我只担心你看得太透。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"看得太透，就看不到“自己”了。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"不过是在这里耕种罢了。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"山水草木皆有情，这一草一木在你看来，也未必和我们的生命有什么区别。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"你还有什么放不下的东西呢，你还会在意什么呢？","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"颉曾经也留下过那么多书卷字帖，她希望能教每个人读书识字。但她走后，那些字帖书文也一同消失，除了我们，没人记得她。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"可后来我去过几所学堂，还有天师府，看到有些书本中用的字迹，竟和她的一模一样。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"她那些东西早都没有了，连我都没能留下哪怕一张，但她说过的话又从那些学生的嘴里说了出来，写过的字又在那些学生的笔下复现。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我记得她和我说过，“重要的是我能留下来的”。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......我只是在看，这片稻田的尽头，能留下什么。如果有一日我也消散了，我能为这里留下什么。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"你一直在看着的那个结局，有变化吗？","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"白茫茫一片大雪，从来没有变过。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......春种秋收，繁盛过后，最终都被一场大雪掩埋。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"这样啊......","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"对这个结果，你会失望吗？还是觉得遗憾？","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"来这世间走过一遭，这本身不就是结果？","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"就像这世上无数人一样，有谁是想着生命有一个终点，便无所适从了呢。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"令","text":"可是，我们有的兄弟不这么想......那位弟弟，他回来了？","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_avg_2023_ling_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"嗯。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":88},{"type":"multiline","name":"令","text":"原来那个胆小又乖巧的绩去哪里了呢？","id":89},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_2023_ling_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":90},{"type":"multiline","name":"令","text":"唉，这些弟弟妹妹，还是小时候比较可爱。","id":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......我会去见见他。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":94},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":95},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":97},{"type":"bgeffect","id":98},{"type":"charslot","id":99},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_bg_47_g3_fieldpath.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","id":101},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":103},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_normal_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":104,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"一、二、三......","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"大嗓门，这些到底是什么新品种啊？我好像从来没见过，长得还怪好看的。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"说了你也听不懂，别多嘴，帮我找就对了。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"嘁，叫人帮忙还这么大脾气......","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"对了大嗓门，我还想问你一个事情......","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"你不是天师府的学徒吗，而且我认识的人里，除了黍姐姐和小禾，就数你懂得最多了。","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"你要问什么，赶紧说啊。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......你......有没有见过我的爸爸妈妈？","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"......","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c2/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":126},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"25","ystrength":"25","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"*炎国粗口*天师府上上下下多少人，你以为我是门卫大爷，把每个人都记得清清楚楚？！","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"脑子被泥砸傻了吧你！","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"不知道就不知道嘛，干嘛突然凶人。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"你为啥想起来要问我这个？","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"今天我见到了一个奇怪的商人，他说他是从大荒城外面，从很远的地方来的。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"哦？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"黍姐姐说，我的爸妈也是去很远的地方当天师了。但是不知道他们到底是去做什么，这么多年都没回来，也从来没有听别人说起过。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"大嗓门，你真的不能帮我打听打听吗？","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"也不用让他们回来，我就是想写封信告诉他们，大荒城快搬家了，搬上了移动地块。他们回家的时候别找不到路。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"......","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"......行了，瞎操的哪份心。你当天师府是什么地方，到该回家的时候，肯定有人带他们回家的。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"唔......","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"洪水影响过的地块，就到这里为止了吧？","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":149},{"type":"multiline","name":"小满","text":"好像是的......","id":150},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":151},{"type":"multiline","name":"小满","text":"怎么了？你要找的这种水稻，和洪水有关系吗？","id":152},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"不该问的别问，天师府的工作，说了你也不明白。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"神气什么！小禾说过，只要我耐着性子多看几本书，凭我的源石技艺天赋，肯定也能考上天师府的！","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/92/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"好好，那就等你考上了再说吧。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"还有，我托你找水稻这件事，千万别和别人讲啊。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":161},{"type":"multiline","name":"小满","text":"为......","id":162},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":163},{"type":"multiline","name":"小满","text":"算了，你肯定不会说的。","id":164},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"喂......你最近，过得还好？有没有受欺负？","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我......挺开心的呀。小禾和黍姐姐都挺照顾我，职农大伯大婶们人也很好，最近还认识了小烛台和小毛笔两个新朋友......","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"这是什么问题？你关心我？","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"谁关心你这个野丫头！","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"得了，今天还是辛苦你了，照顾好自己吧。","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"天师学徒","text":"下次要是有人欺负你，你就照我教你的，用笛子敲他的头！","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":176},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"bgeffect","id":180},{"type":"charslot","id":181},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_bg_47_g12_cityoperastage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15side/m_sys_bitw_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":184,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"桑麻日已长，我土日已广......","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"敢教邪祟诡魔辟易，天地焕新光......","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"啦......啦......","id":189},{"type":"dialog","id":190},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.8","channel":"step","loop":"false","id":191},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"step","fadetime":"2","id":192},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":193},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":194},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"......","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我一直不喜欢这尊塑像。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"谁说“神农”就一定得是短褐穿结，饱经风霜的样子？明明她也是很爱美的，她总是在发髻上戴着花，也很喜欢我做的衣裳。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"而且，我记得很清楚，她的眼睛，和你很像。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"要是能让夕给她留下一幅画像该多好......可惜那个时候，夕好像也还没有学会画画。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","volume":"0.8","channel":"step1","loop":"false","id":202},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"step1","fadetime":"2","id":203},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":204},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":205},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我以为你不会再回来了。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"再怎么讲我也不是离家出走的年纪，我又什么时候说过不会回来的话？","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"游子漂泊在外久了总会想家的，想来想去，也只有这里能算我的家了。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#17$1","focus":"r","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"偏偏是这个时候？","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"要是能早两天回来，还能赶上今年的社戏，再尝尝你包的麦穗饺子。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"可以啊，“远行的饺子，回家的面”，想吃什么，家里都有。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"吃完饭，就又该上路了。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"怎么我才留下不到两天，就这么急着赶我走？","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你要是只是回来歇歇，想留多久都可以。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"就是想问问你，你真的只是回来歇歇的吗？","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"......","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"每次回来，大荒城都要变一番模样。谁还能想到，千年前这里还是一片冻土的样子。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"是人们从紧挨着邪祟诡魔的地方抢下了这一片土地。那时候，山河混沌，天无四时，但是人心明亮。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"人们不分身份，不分国别，相互扶持，敌人只有眼前的荒地，还有不知什么时候会出现的邪魔。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"前几天，我还梦见过她，也梦见过那位老先生。所以我想，可能是时候回来看看了。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"所幸还能找到回家的路，只可惜......人心不古。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你又有多久，没好好看过这里的人了。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"天下熙熙，皆为利来；天下攘攘，皆为利往。","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"利在哪，人就在哪。哪都一样。","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"事到如今，你觉得朝廷里的人，商量的到底是如何保住我们一家人的性命，还是如何寻求一个对他们而言最稳妥的局面？","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"......你真的相信，年的那个造物，可以保所有人的平安？","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"这是唯一可以保大家性命的办法。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"这是把性命交到别人手里。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"双方合伙做生意，有利一起赚，风险却只有一边承担。这不是一笔合算买卖，至少不是笔公平的买卖。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"要想生意做得长久，那至少要让两方背着一样的风险才行。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"远行了这么久，你在意的就只有账本上的盈亏了？","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我在意的是你。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"姐姐，你累了。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"为这里的一草一木操劳还不够，又帮年去做那个工程，是很耗神的。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"不然的话，这次的事，你本该更早发现的。","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"千年来，无数次天灾，每一次，天灾降临在这片土地上，你都会提前知道......这片土地上的一切，你都会感同身受。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"你到底在坚持些什么？","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"事到如今，谁才是逆天而行的那一个？","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":261},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"charslot","id":264},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_bg_47_g8_crestofweir.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":265},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":266},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":267},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_darkness_03_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":268,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":270},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"醒醒！","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"告诉我，你看到了什么？","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"charslot","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":277},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"1","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":280},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我看到了......什么......？","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我看到了......","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"等等......你怎么知道？","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"charslot","id":288},{"type":"text","text":"左乐手上捻着一缕丝线，眼看着它很快消失在了空气中。","id":289},{"type":"dialog","id":290},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#3$2","focus":"m","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"可能是有人在恶作剧......大概是源石技艺吧......","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5e/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-3$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2","focus":"m","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你看到的那些东西应该是你自己的幻觉，但有他想让你看到的东西，就像是某种心理暗示......你看到了什么？","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我好像看到了一位老农，他......或者是她？","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"让我在地里耕种。我种不出庄稼，但是越来越老，再没力气拿起锄头......","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"还有河对岸的树上挂着不少木牌，那边没人过去过，但我看到了上面好像写着人名......那个老农也消失了。","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2","focus":"m","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......河对岸？","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"他让你看到河对岸......","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-10$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":302},{"type":"charslot","id":303},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":304},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_wind","volume":"0.7","id":305},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_breezetree","volume":"0.4","delay":"0.3","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":307},{"type":"text","text":"禾生叹了口气，顺着河流向远处眺望。","id":308},{"type":"text","text":"河对岸的树木郁郁葱葱，一阵风刮过，似乎还能听到树叶沙沙作响的声音。","id":309},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.6","channel":"mstep","loop":"false","id":311},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"mstep","fadetime":"2","id":312},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","duration":"1","id":313},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"小禾，小烛台，你们在这？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2f/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#6$2","focus":"m","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"小满姑娘！你到哪里去了？！","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-6$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我刚刚找水稻来着......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"找水稻？你不是去找牧兽了？什么水稻需要专门去找？","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我——","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1","id":326},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"charslot","id":329},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_bg_47_g3_fieldpath.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1238_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":332},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":333},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":334},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":335},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的天师学徒","text":"还有，我托你找水稻这件事，千万别和别人讲啊。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/05/Avg_avg_npc_1238_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":338},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"charslot","id":341},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_bg_47_g8_crestofweir.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":345},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":348},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我答应过别人......要保密的......","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"奇奇怪怪......怎么尽是让人摸不着头脑的事......","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"是谁要你找水稻？什么样子的水稻？在哪里找到的？","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"小烛台？你怎么这么紧张......有点吓人......","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"25","ystrength":"25","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"小满姑娘！","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-5$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"好好好我说......","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"是一个天师府的小个子学生......说要找特殊品种的水稻用来交作业......","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"我也不知道是什么种类......只是看上去像是红色的，红得发黑......在堰口有一些，离这不远的水田里也有一些。","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"1","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":367},{"type":"charslot","id":368},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_47_i05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":369},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":373},{"type":"dialog","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"image","id":377},{"type":"charslot","id":378},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7a/Avg_bg_47_g8_crestofweir.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":380},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","id":381},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":382},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"1","id":384},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"小满","text":"......","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_4122_grabds_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"小禾，前些日子收上来的粮食都放在哪里？","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"大荒城有集中的粮仓，在核心城里。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"能请你现在就去查看一下粮仓吗？如果有什么异状，立刻去找老乡长。","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"等等......到底是什么事这么着急？","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2","focus":"m","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"恐怕已经来不及了......","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_avg_4121_zuole_1-4$2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"charslot","id":402},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_bg_47_g12_cityoperastage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","id":404},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":406},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":408},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"现在的社戏一共是三出，《大狩天》《争天时》《万物生》。","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"但很早之前，在第一、二出之间应该还有一出《度北疆》，很久都不唱了。","id":411,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"姐姐，你还记得该怎么唱吗？能不能再唱一段？","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"调子还记得，词已经差不多忘了。","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"都是陈年旧事，没什么好唱的。","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"是啊，台下没有观众，唱戏也没劲。","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"过眼就忘的戏，看起来也没劲。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":420},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":421,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"可我还记得......","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我还记得，北方的这一块邪魔碎片，是当时的人不择手段寻来对付祂的方法，祂的化身如今却在帮人们抵挡邪魔的灾害。实在是有趣。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我们早就不该再和祂混为一谈。","id":427,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"的确不该。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"邪祟诡魔，绝不能为普通百姓所知，但偏偏一片罕见的少受源石污染的土地就在这里，实在没法放弃。","id":430,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"一千年来，这里的人们就生活在与那片秽土一河之隔的地方。人们也真的在这里埋头耕作，不问世事，持续了一千年。","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"有因有果。千年前，人们自己种下的因，现在，也该有人来摘这个果了。还得是合适的人才行。","id":433,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......告诉我，那场灾害，和你无关，对吗？","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"我何时对你说过假话？","id":437,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#17$1","focus":"r","id":438},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"只是有时候会选择不说真话。","id":439,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......你这次回来，到底是想做什么？","id":440,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1236_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"就像我刚才说的，只是回家看看。","id":442,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"绩","text":"还是和以前一样，只是想问问你，姐姐，要不要和我一起走？","id":443,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_1236_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#17$1","focus":"r","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那我的回答也是和以前一样，我不会离开，也不想离开。","id":445,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/67/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-17$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":446},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":447},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":448},{"type":"charslot","id":449},{"type":"image","id":450}],"characters":["黍","令","小满","暴躁的天师学徒","天师学徒","绩","左乐","禾生"]}